<br>
There is another part of the shaman epic quest which follows that right there in North Freeport. It involves following Bondl out of the sewers and to a tavern. Don't bother going. I did it once last night and completed the whole next part of the epic and you don't get any more Truespirit faction bumps during that part. Just stick with the initial exchanges up to Bondl and you'll do fine. <p>Jakiss, 54 Channeler of Xev<br>
